<note n="0162001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0162001">「備矢携水筒」，採用暹羅本之 sajjitaṁ dhanum ādāya pakkhittasalilaṁ。</note>
<note n="0163001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0163001">「我等無利得」，採用暹羅本之 lābho mayhaṁ na vijjati。</note>
<note n="0168001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0168001">「以淨信心」，底本為 pasanno sehi pāṇihi，親手為何意義不明。暹羅本為 vippasasannecetasā，今則更應讀為 vippasannenacetasā。</note>
<note n="0168002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0168002">「意思無不適」，採用脚註異本及暹羅本 anūnamanasaṅkappo。</note>
<note n="0168003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0168003">三種之火採用脚註異本及暹羅本之 tidhaggī。</note>
<note n="0170001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0170001">「獨住」，採用暹羅本之 ekekaṁ。</note>
<note n="0178001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0178001">「由佛知宿業」，採用暹羅本之 pubbakammaṁ vibhāvitaṁ。</note>
<note n="0179002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0179002">「宿世非淨緣」，暹羅本參照，讀為 patipubbe na-visuddhipaccayā。</note>
<note n="0181001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0181001">採用脚註異本及暹羅本之 dharissati。</note>
<note n="0181002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0181002">採用暹羅本之 sammatālasamāhitaṁ。</note>
